Sniper/Rhinox


Sniper Steped out of the cr chamber. He walked to the comand center
of 
the ark. He sees Rhinox sitting down by the scanners. "Get up, we
need 
to repair the ark, In case of an attack."

Rhinox stood up. "Yes, sir." He said 'sir' because he knew Sniper 
probally had higher rank them him.

Sniper looked at Rhinox. "Don't call me sir, I have no power. Now 
get."

Rhinox walked out of the ark and started reparing the base.

Sniper started to walk out of the ark when he noticed Lino leaving 
with Tigerhawk. He called to Iron Raptor. "Where's Lino going, Iron."
